snippet.title: WHAT REMAINS OF EDITH FINCH | Available Now On Xbox Series X|S + PS5
snippet.description:
What Remains of Edith Finch is now available natively for Xbox Series X|S and PS5 with 4K and 60FPS support. Current Xbox One and PS4 owners can upgrade for free.

Developed by GIANT SPARROW. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2022
